    public abstract class AbstractRichCombinedFilterFunction<T>
extends org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.RichFilterFunction<T>
implements CombinableFilter<T>
    A RichFilterFunction that can be combined like a CombinableFilter. The context will be handled for each filter that is part of this combined filter.
